      "review_summary": "This PR adds a typed WhatsApp monitor socket-factory override through the connection controller and monitor path, exports the setter/types from `@openclaw/whatsapp/api.js`, and adds controller coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +50, Tests +46. Total +96 across 7 files.\n\nReproducibility: not applicable. this is a QA/runtime feature PR rather than a reported bug. Source inspection verifies current main opens the real WhatsApp socket directly, while the PR head adds an optional injected factory path.",
